<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>ERP</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" th:href="@{/css/index_css.css}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="dashboard-container">
    <!-- 사이드바: 모든 페이지 공통 -->
    <nav class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo">
            <i class="fas fa-code"></i> 
            <span>Dev Pro</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/main" class="active"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> main </a></li>
            <li><a href="/project"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 프로젝트 현황</a></li>
            <li><a href="/members"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> 팀원 관리</a></li>
            <li><a href="/settings"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> 시스템 설정</a></li>
            <li><a href="/help"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> 도움말</a></li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="user-profile">
            <span class="user-info">관리자님</span>
            <div class="auth-links">
                <a href="/login">로그인</a>
                <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 메인 콘텐츠: 페이지별로 변경되는 영역 -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="welcome-card">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt fa-3x"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-text">
                <h1>환영합니다, 관리자님!</h1>
                <p>왼쪽 메뉴를 선택하여 대시보드 항목을 확인하세요.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">오늘 방문자: 1,284</div>
            <div class="stat-card">활성 프로젝트: 5</div>
            <div class="stat-card">시스템 알림: 3</div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

</body>
</html>